A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Toles, Temple & Wright, Inc., as the 2025 Heart of the
2 Community Business Award recipient; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Toles, Temple & Wright, Inc., is a locally owned, second-generation real estate
4 brokerage established in 1972; and
5 WHEREAS, Toles, Temple & Wright, Inc., fosters a culture where agents and staff are
6 encouraged and empowered to invest their time and resources to support and enhance the
7 area's vibrant quality of life; and
8 WHEREAS, Toles, Temple & Wright, Inc., Real Estate agents and staff often serve the
9 community by providing Christmas gifts and clothing for Pre-K children from disadvantaged
10 families and by volunteering and donating time and service to Salvation Army, Davies
11 Shelters, P.A.W.S., Victims of Summerville floods and Hurricane Helene, Adopt-a-Mile
12 clean-up projects with Keep Rome-Floyd Beautiful, Brighter Birthdays, Cancer Navigators,
13 Fork Spoon & Plate Hunger Ministry, Chiaha Harvest Festival, Coosa River Basin Initiative,
14 Rome Shakespeare Festival, Sexual Assault Center, South Rome Alliance, and YMCA
15 Arsenal Soccer Club; and
