16 WHEREAS, individual members of the Toles, Temple & Wright, Inc., team have been
17 recognized for humanitarian efforts with Heart of the Community Awards of Honor,
18 Exchange Club Family Resource Center, and the Greater Rome Board of Realtors; and
19 WHEREAS, members of the Toles, Temple & Wright, Inc,. team have been appointed to
20 serve on governmental bodies to include Greenway Partnership, Housing Authority, Parks
21 & Recreation, Planning Commission and Special Committee on Housing as well as various
22 school auxiliary organizations.
23 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
24 the members of this body recognize Toles, Temple & Wright, Inc., Real Estate for its
25 outstanding dedication to the community, commend Toles, Temple & Wright, Inc., Real
26 Estate as a recipient of the 2025 Heart of the Community Business Award, and extend the
27 most sincere best wishes for continued success.
28 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
29 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Toles,
30 Temple & Wright, Inc.
